{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877955677,"sessionID":"ses_2856d0f1affeCOzvGfZgcTf2Ts","part":{"id":"prt_d7a931d8000107mnxyK7lLna44","messageID":"msg_d7a931102001vZCqhXxcbpKrM7","sessionID":"ses_2856d0f1affeCOzvGfZgcTf2Ts","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3e00ba54322f452392f6146ec733a7ce","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Delta Specification\n2: \n3: ## Change Summary\n4: \n5: This AR introduces a new SDK client for the AgentRuntime service, enabling Python applications to manage agents and their runtime sessions programmatically.\n6: \n7: ## New API Endpoints\n8: \n9: ### Agent Management\n10: \n11: - `POST /v1/agents` - Create a new agent\n12: - `GET /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Retrieve agent details\n13: - `GET /v1/agents` - List agents with optional filtering\n14: - `PUT /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Update agent configuration\n15: - `DELETE /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Delete an agent\n16: \n17: ### Runtime Operations\n18: \n19: - `POST /v1/agents/{agent_id}/start` - Start an agent execution session\n20: - `POST /v1/sessions/{session_id}/stop` - Stop a running session\n21: - `GET /v1/sessions/{session_id}` - Get session status and details\n22: - `GET /v1/sessions` - List sessions with optional filtering\n23: \n24: ## New Data Models\n25: \n26: ### Agent\n27: \n28: ```python\n29: {\n30:   \"agent_id\": str,\n31:   \"workspace_id\": str,\n32:   \"name\": str,\n33:   \"description\": Optional[str],\n34:   \"config\": AgentConfig,\n35:   \"status\": AgentStatus,\n36:   \"created_at\": datetime,\n37:   \"updated_at\": datetime,\n38:   \"metadata\": Dict[str, str]\n39: }\n40: ```\n41: \n42: ### AgentConfig\n43: \n44: ```python\n45: {\n46:   \"runtime_config\": RuntimeConfig,\n47:   \"capabilities\": List[str],\n48:   \"constraints\": Optional[Dict[str, Any]],\n49:   \"resources\": Optional[ResourceConfig]\n50: }\n51: ```\n52: \n53: ### RuntimeSession\n54: \n55: ```python\n56: {\n57:   \"session_id\": str,\n58:   \"agent_id\": str,\n59:   \"status\": SessionStatus,\n60:   \"input_data\": Optional[Dict[str, Any]],\n61:   \"output_data\": Optional[Dict[str, Any]],\n62:   \"started_at\": datetime,\n63:   \"completed_at\": Optional[datetime],\n64:   \"error_message\": Optional[str]\n65: }\n66: ```\n67: \n68: ## New Enums\n69: \n70: ### AgentStatus\n71: \n72: - `CREATING` - Agent is being created\n73: - `ACTIVE` - Agent is active and ready\n74: - `STOPPED` - Agent is stopped\n75: - `ERROR` - Agent encountered an error\n76: - `DELETED` - Agent has been deleted\n77: \n78: ### SessionStatus\n79: \n80: - `STARTING` - Session is starting\n81: - `RUNNING` - Session is running\n82: - `COMPLETED` - Session completed successfully\n83: - `STOPPED` - Session was stopped\n84: - `ERROR` - Session encountered an error\n85: \n86: ## New Exceptions\n87: \n88: ### AgentRuntimeException (base)\n89: - `AuthenticationError` - Authentication failed\n90: - `ConnectionError` - Connection to service failed\n91: - `AgentError` (base)\n92:   - `AgentCreationError` - Failed to create agent\n93:   - `AgentNotFoundError` - Agent not found\n94:   - `AgentUpdateError` - Failed to update agent\n95: - `RuntimeError` (base)\n96:   - `SessionNotFoundError` - Session not found\n97:   - `ExecutionError` - Runtime execution failed\n98: - `ValidationError` - Input validation failed\n99: \n100: ## Backward Compatibility\n101: \n102: This change introduces entirely new functionality and does not modify existing APIs. It is fully backward compatible.\n103: \n104: ## Migration Notes\n105: \n106: No migration required. This is a new feature addition.\n107: \n108: ## Dependencies\n109: \n110: This change depends on:\n111: - `httpx` >= 0.24.0\n112: - `pydantic` >= 2.0.0\n113: - Python >= 3.9\n114: \n115: ## Breaking Changes\n116: \n117: None. This is a new feature.\n\n(End of file - total 117 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Delta Specification\n\n## Change Summary\n\nThis AR introduces a new SDK client for the AgentRuntime service, enabling Python applications to manage agents and their runtime sessions programmatically.\n\n## New API Endpoints\n\n### Agent Management\n\n- `POST /v1/agents` - Create a new agent\n- `GET /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Retrieve agent details\n- `GET /v1/agents` - List agents with optional filtering\n- `PUT /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Update agent configuration\n- `DELETE /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Delete an agent\n\n### Runtime Operations\n\n- `POST /v1/agents/{agent_id}/start` - Start an agent execution session\n- `POST /v1/sessions/{session_id}/stop` - Stop a running session","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775877955663,"end":1775877955675}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877955681,"sessionID":"ses_2856d0f1affeCOzvGfZgcTf2Ts","part":{"id":"prt_d7a932035001LXCQqcp73fwkV5","messageID":"msg_d7a931102001vZCqhXxcbpKrM7","sessionID":"ses_2856d0f1affeCOzvGfZgcTf2Ts","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-cb667732eaf84345abe2ac3fc1142084","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Delta Specification\n2: \n3: ## Delta from Base System\n4: \n5: ### New Module: python-sdk/code_interpreter\n6: \n7: This change introduces a new Python SDK module for the CodeInterpreter service.\n8: \n9: ### New Files\n10: \n11: 1. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/client.py**\n12:    - Main CodeInterpreterClient class implementation\n13:    - Session management methods\n14:    - Code execution methods\n15:    - HTTP client wrapper\n16: \n17: 2. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/models.py**\n18:    - Data model definitions (Session, ExecutionResult, ExecutionJob)\n19:    - Enum definitions (SessionStatus, ExecutionStatus)\n20:    - Pydantic models for validation\n21: \n22: 3. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/exceptions.py**\n23:    - Custom exception hierarchy\n24:    - Error messages and error codes\n25: \n26: 4. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/__init__.py**\n27:    - Module exports\n28:    - Public API surface\n29: \n30: ### Dependencies Added\n31: \n32: - **httpx ^0.24.0**: HTTP client for async requests\n33: - **pydantic ^2.0.0**: Data validation and serialization\n34: \n35: ### API Changes\n36: \n37: **New Public API:**\n38: \n39: ```python\n40: from agentcube.sdk import CodeInterpreterClient, Session, ExecutionResult\n41: \n42: client = CodeInterpreterClient(base_url=\"http://localhost:8080\")\n43: session = await client.create_session(workspace_id=\"workspace-123\")\n44: result = await client.execute_code(session.session_id, code=\"print('Hello')\")\n45: ```\n46: \n47: ### Backward Compatibility\n48: \n49: This is a new module with no breaking changes to existing functionality.\n50: \n51: ### Integration Points\n52: \n53: - Uses existing python-sdk infrastructure (if any)\n54: - Follows project coding standards\n55: - Integrates with project testing framework\n56: \n57: ### Configuration Changes\n58: \n59: No configuration changes required in existing components.\n60: \n61: ### Deployment Impact\n62: \n63: - New Python package module\n64: - Requires CodeInterpreter service to be deployed\n65: - No changes to existing services\n\n(End of file - total 65 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Delta Specification\n\n## Delta from Base System\n\n### New Module: python-sdk/code_interpreter\n\nThis change introduces a new Python SDK module for the CodeInterpreter service.\n\n### New Files\n\n1. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/client.py**\n   - Main CodeInterpreterClient class implementation\n   - Session management methods\n   - Code execution methods\n   - HTTP client wrapper\n\n2. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/models.py**\n   - Data model definitions (Session, ExecutionResult, ExecutionJob)\n   - Enum definitions (SessionStatus, ExecutionStatus)\n   - Pydantic models for validation","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775877955666,"end":1775877955678}}}}
